73","tid":2185642,"uid":5763,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:46:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9C%AB%E6%97%A5%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2580%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=daece935\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9C%AB%E6%97%A5%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%80%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n岩岩走去wiki,發覺好多人呃飯食,都未中過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"中呀！今次深山中呀！"},{"pid":"568d82ba5eae539bacb42133b7a0a6483f14d546","tid":2185642,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"2019<br />\n2020<br />\n咁多大事有咩中過?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434489eeb2e01900075ffb2a4113a3195a8adfe9","tid":2185642,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近呢十年<br />\n地球究竟經歷左幾多次世界末日？<br />\n點解我仲生存緊"},{"pid":"2716b18ac9fe194c5aec52a18dd2843f04e28885","tid":2185642,"uid":309553,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T11:54:53.000Z","msg":"睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"f42ba90a5289d660095561075746